text: Kembangan MRT Station (EW6) is an MRT Station in Singapore. It is along the East West MRT Line. The station is above-ground with platform screen doors. ==Timeline== *4 November 1989: Station opened ==Following stations== Previous: Bedok (EW5) Next: Eunos (EW7) ==Former codes== Formerly the Code was: E7 (1989 - 2001) Category:1989 establishments in Singapore Category:Mass Rapid Transit (Singapore) stations
title: Kembangan MRT station
